            <paragraph classes="classref-method" ids="class-inputevent-method-is-pressed" names="class_inputevent_method_is_pressed"><reference internal="True" refuri="class_bool#class-bool"><inline classes="std std-ref">bool</inline></reference> <strong>is_pressed</strong>() <abbreviation explanation="This method has no side effects. It doesn't modify any of the instance's member variables.">const</abbreviation> <reference internal="True" refid="class-inputevent-method-is-pressed"><inline classes="std std-ref">ðŸ”—</inline></reference></paragraph>
            <paragraph>Returns <literal>true</literal> if this input event is pressed. Not relevant for events of type <reference internal="True" refuri="class_inputeventmousemotion#class-inputeventmousemotion"><inline classes="std std-ref">InputEventMouseMotion</inline></reference> or <reference internal="True" refuri="class_inputeventscreendrag#class-inputeventscreendrag"><inline classes="std std-ref">InputEventScreenDrag</inline></reference>.</paragraph>
            <paragraph><strong>Note:</strong> Due to keyboard ghosting, <reference internal="True" refid="class-inputevent-method-is-pressed"><inline classes="std std-ref">is_pressed()</inline></reference> may return <literal>false</literal> even if one of the action's keys is pressed. See <reference name="Input examples" refuri="../tutorials/inputs/input_examples.html#keyboard-events">Input examples</reference> in the documentation for more information.</paragraph>
            <transition classes="classref-item-separator"></transition>
            <target refid="class-inputevent-method-is-released"></target>
            <paragraph classes="classref-method" ids="class-inputevent-method-is-released" names="class_inputevent_method_is_released"><reference internal="True" refuri="class_bool#class-bool"><inline classes="std std-ref">bool</inline></reference> <strong>is_released</strong>() <abbreviation explanation="This method has no side effects. It doesn't modify any of the instance's member variables.">const</abbreviation> <reference internal="True" refid="class-inputevent-method-is-released"><inline classes="std std-ref">ðŸ”—</inline></reference></paragraph>
